{"tid":1540783,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"袋住先？四大訴求？","createTime":"2019-09-04T12:32:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T12:55:30.000Z","uid":160693,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b604494e0c2e7f8dd6240bb2028ee03e6c592254","tid":1540783,"uid":160693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:32:00.000Z","msg":"林鄭只是標題黨，沒有正式撤回。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢只係叫保安局局長，係下一個行政年度提出撤回動議。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家唔好唔記得，議會條例係一七年嘅時候已經修改，基本上泛民係冇任何拉布嘅可能性，亦唔洗講泛民唔夠議席，因為之前一班本土議員俾佢DQ 曬。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以，到時提出&ldquo;撤回&rdquo; 動議，建制班人反對&ldquo;撤回&rdquo;，咁就可以安排二三讀一齊。到時求其造個juicy d 新聞 ，條例過咗大家先知。<br />\n<br />\n袋住先？四大訴求？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n幾日後美國國會 ，就會話已經under control，唔理我地，喊都冇用。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n外國人唔知香港政府手段，以為香港人成功咗。再嘈，無病呻吟。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n根本就係個局，係9月8號之前令到大家嘅民憤冇咁勁。到十月嘅時候先發現俾人呃咗，美國國會嗰邊已經唔會再理你地啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有，佢到而家佢都冇講過831太子究竟發生左咩事，如果真係死咗入，冇人提起，冇人知真相，到底係咪真係有人犧牲咗，個３個人到底係唔係示威者，定只不過係太子要轉車嘅乘客。呢ｄ冇人會知。佢地變咗condom 啊。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人，林鄭撚你咋。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a24124420b0ed8f6b0c2344a741e00feeb52f1e","tid":1540783,"uid":20059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:32:47.000Z","msg":"（突發）民間記者會普及方法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1540686\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1540686</a><br />\n入黎幫手推"},{"pid":"e21e4bc3f1b9bc97597d5902080b06a5eca71e97","tid":1540783,"uid":160693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:33:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e3f0694fc17ed7548b702587d37b41d4e78dbc04","tid":1540783,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:33:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ec4639bd7642fa2c6856e6ae4e9bb27ec5820820","tid":1540783,"uid":275634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:34:09.000Z","msg":"緩兵之計，借機清算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n將個波踢比立法會奶共派，即係否決撤回<br />\n<img src=\"/a